{
  "meta": {
    "ep": 3,
    "title": "The Glass",
    "kind": "main"
  },
  "messages": [
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "This is awkward.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "awkward", "index": 2, "definition": "尴尬的", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I should not be watching this.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "But what's the protocol?",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "\"Excuse me, I heard you sacrifice your happiness — ketchup please?\"",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "No. Stay invisible. That's my specialty.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Through the gap between booths — I can see everything.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Anna stands frozen, staring at the door Sousuke bolted through.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "No performance now. Just the raw aftermath.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "aftermath", "index": 6, "definition": "后果", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The decision her mouth made while her heart screamed the opposite.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "She sits down. Not her seat. His.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "She reaches across the table.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Her hand closes around Sousuke's glass.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The one he was drinking from. Minutes ago.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "She lifts it with both hands. Like something fragile.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "fragile", "index": 8, "definition": "脆弱的", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Don't. Don't do something that sad.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "She puts the straw to her lips. Drinks.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "An indirect kiss.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "With a guy sprinting toward another girl.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "A ritual of acceptance. Or surrender.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "ritual", "index": 1, "definition": "仪式", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I'm not smart enough to know which.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Just the most bittersweet thing I've ever seen.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "bittersweet", "index": 3, "definition": "苦乐参半的", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Her eyes lift. Through the gap. Straight into mine.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "One frozen moment. Two statues in a restaurant.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Anna's cheeks go pink, then crimson.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Her eyes widen with the slow-motion horror of recognition.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "recognition", "index": 8, "definition": "认出", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "It's now painfully evident she's seen everything.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "evident", "index": 3, "definition": "明显的", "is_new": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "PFFFT— A brown explosion across her table.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Anna Yanami — cutest girl in class — coughing, choking on coffee.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Making sounds no grace could salvage.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "grace", "index": 3, "definition": "优雅", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Decision time. Born of pure cowardice.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I raise my soda.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Attempt to look absorbed in the menu. Which is upside down.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "absorbed", "index": 3, "definition": "全神贯注的", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I try to whistle. I've never whistled in my life.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The result sounds like a medical episode.",
      "marks": [
        { "word": "episode", "index": 6, "definition": "事件, 插曲", "is_new": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Footsteps approach. A shadow falls across my table.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "side": "left",
      "name": "Anna",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "side": "left",
      "name": "Anna",
      "text": "You're Nukumizu, right? Class C?",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "This is the moment my quiet invisible life ends.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "side": "right",
      "name": "Kazuhiko",
      "text": "...Nukumizu who?",
      "marks": []
    }
  ],
